column2: SELECT TOP #  p.petroR9#Err_g, p.petroR9#_g, p.petroR9#Err_r, p.petroR9#_r,   p.petroR9#Err_i, p.petroR9#_i,   p.petroR5#Err_g, p.petroR5#_g, p.petroR5#Err_r, p.petroR5#_r,   p.petroR5#Err_i, p.petroR5#_i,   s.vdisp_median, s.vdisp_err,  s.mstellar_median, s.mstellar_err FROM PhotoObjall AS p  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS s ON s.specobjid = p.objid WHERE   p.petroR9#Err_g > # and petroR9#_g > #*p.petroR9#Err_g and   p.petroR9#Err_r > # and petroR9#_r > #*p.petroR9#Err_r and  p.petroR9#Err_i > # and petroR9#_i > #*p.petroR9#Err_i and   p.petroR5#Err_g > # and petroR5#_g > #*p.petroR5#Err_g and   p.petroR5#Err_r > # and petroR5#_r > #*p.petroR5#Err_r and  p.petroR5#Err_i > # and petroR5#_i > #*p.petroR5#Err_i and   petroR5#_g/petroR9#_g <# and petroR5#_g/petroR9#_g > # and   petroR5#_r/petroR9#_r <# and petroR5#_r/petroR9#_r > # and  petroR5#_i/petroR9#_i <# and petroR5#_i/petroR9#_i > #
